  dialogueLines:
  - "I would tell you to go find a circus, but you\u2019re already here, hahah~!"
  - "Funny\u2026 You\u2019re the clown of this circus?"
  - ' Not a clown, but a Jester!'
  - But I do like jokes!
  - "Oh god\u2026"
  - What do you call a magic dog?
  - A Labracadabrador!!
  - "...ok that\u2019s pretty good. "
  - ' I know it is!'
  - 'Next: What did the shark say when he ate the clownfish? '
  - That it tasted funny?
  - HAHAHAHA~!! YES~~!!!
  - Last one!
  - ' How many clowns do you need to take down the tent?'
  - I don't know.
  - None, because the show will go on forever!!!
  - "and ever, and ever .....and ever\u2026\u2026\u2026............"
  - .......
  - Hahah~ I hope you have fun~~!
  - Yeeeah... hahah... byeeee
  - No, don't leave yet, we still have to play!!!
  - Voi nyt vittu-
